{
  "stem": "21310.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were in this-- it was called [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was really-- it came-- [POLISH] is the Polish word for it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It means cauldron.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cauldron-- C-A-U-L-D-R-O-N.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it comes from a German word.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was called [GERMAN], you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [GERMAN] was being surrounded, being, being taken into a small place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But somehow from that, it came into Polish that the castle is like a cauldron.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's what they called this one experience.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was in September of 1942, and where all people had to go to, to this particular place where the selection was taking place.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And only people who worked at the time had some ID card, some statement, some certificate that they were working, supposedly were left in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the other ones were deported.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now there were some people who never went when the call came to come, to come to this place, who didn't come and were hiding.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But many of them were killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because the Germans and the police and there was Latvian or Ukrainian police going from building to building and searching for people who were, were in the apartments.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So some people hid and didn't go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But most of the people had to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there were some, there were some horrid things were going on at this, at this time, at this so-called selection.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remember children were not illegal anymore and-- cause they were not productive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we had-- so some people were trying to smuggle their children through the-- in, in knapsacks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They gave them something to sleep and-- because there was still pharmacists in, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they knew how to, you know-- they had some pills and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
